{"tid":1428541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全民練EQ！有屌過藍絲嘅同我入嚟！","createTime":"2019-08-07T10:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T06:19:39.000Z","uid":296759,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"81a81374e7bcf87d7e281aca5f61a06b0189e19c","tid":1428541,"uid":296759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:08:20.000Z","msg":"近排班狗好似癲狗咁見人就咬，其實係我哋<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民意大反攻好機會！！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">將佢哋濫捕、濫權、蝦細佬、爆記者頭同拉議員呢啲黑材料<span style=\"color: orange;\">無限放大貼落你哋自己區嘅連儂場！</span>！等人知道香港警察同黑社會係無分別！<br />\n<br />\n同時我哋要知，敵人無嘅係EQ同IQ，而呢兩樣係我哋強項！一定要利用！減輕前線壓力！<br />\n<br />\n近幾日睇下班藍絲講乜鳩，佢哋個重點唔再係狗屋玻璃窗爛晒，而係<span style=\"color: orange;\">將黑衫打市民同圍市民喪屌嘅片段不停放大！</span><br />\n<br />\n知唔知點解呀？因為佢哋要將我哋講到同黑社會一鳩樣，從而合理化警狗暴力行為！</span>[size=5]<span style=\"color: red;\">所以千祈唔好中計！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n要記住！香港係和而不同嘅社會！<br />\n對住班滿口歪理嘅人，係會好撚燥！但一定要練高EQ！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔可以做一言堂！！<br />\n唔可以做一言堂！！<br />\n唔可以做一言堂！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. <span style=\"color: blue;\">出口挑釁者</span><br />\n對於出口挑釁嘅藍絲或者屌我哋阻鳩住搵食嘅市民，千祈唔好圍佢或者同佢互屌，你要明白，呢班人唔怕同人嘈交，最怕無人同佢嘈！<br />\n<br />\n所以唔需要都無必要嘈到佢明，只需要好似錄音機咁不停重覆一句</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「政府龜縮 市民上街」<br />\n<br />\n「政府龜縮 市民上街」<br />\n<br />\n「政府龜縮 市民上街」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">將矛頭指返向政府！用喃嘸機式方法不斷講，講到佢哋走！<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: blue;\">出手打人者</span><br />\n對於出手嘅，就一定要還拖，呢個係出於自衛，唔好比人恰！不過都要將前因後果用文宣方法發出去，用輿論對輿論！<br />\n<br />\n唔好話民意唔重要！林鄭不停想搶民意，就知</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">民意其實好緊要！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以！全部人要練高EQ同放大班癲狗做嘅癲事，重申返五大訴求，我哋喺時候拎返民意！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割𥱊不篤灰不指責<br />\n兄弟爬山 各有各做</span></span>"},{"pid":"719bf25f4acab34f40ccaf3d6b5e3c2983bd3348","tid":1428541,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a8cf2589d4a779cd8a3a7138b154c826ee7208","tid":1428541,"uid":296759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:18:35.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b321b414380b2970878fb035d219e48fc1d8f870","tid":1428541,"uid":296759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:27:19.000Z","msg":"我再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />提高EQ治癲狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a10b91412f0c315df08bcc77323075720b7d1bd","tid":1428541,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a79ac9cc5b342fa6f28f800c8e73fa47bed1d18","tid":1428541,"uid":296759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:57:21.000Z","msg":"繼續推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e05bdcd90deeb74618c114a58cf189e54b8aa0c4","tid":1428541,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"884129d19a93461c86057cb1d2d80452fb0493ba","tid":1428541,"uid":81517,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:11:31.000Z","msg":"EQ真係好重要<br />\n尤其宜家我地嘅嘅力量真係俾以前大左好多"},{"pid":"5457cc3cf6694695cd1afc4061991141bf10a4c2","tid":1428541,"uid":296759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:22:05.000Z","msg":"全民練EQ！推呀！<img sr